      "body": "Getting decent throughput when running on my laptop:\r\n```bash\r\n$ FUZZ=scriptpubkeyman ./build_fuzz_nosan/bin/fuzz ../qa-assets/fuzz_corpora/scriptpubkeyman/\r\n...\r\n#3326974\tREDUCE cov: 14175 ft: 84867 corp: 5289/37Mb lim: 998620 exec/s: 1319 rss: 262Mb L: 15776/882699 MS: 1 EraseBytes-\r\n#3327186\tREDUCE cov: 14175 ft: 84867 corp: 5289/37Mb lim: 998620 exec/s: 1319 rss: 262Mb L: 961/882699 MS: 2 ChangeBit-EraseBytes-\r\n#3328687\tREDUCE cov: 14175 ft: 84867 corp: 5289/37Mb lim: 998620 exec/s: 1319 rss: 262Mb L: 1249/882699 MS: 1 EraseBytes-\r\n...\r\n```\r\n\r\nHow is your server configured? Do you see a big speedup after applying this patch?",
